But at least us lowly rally inspired Americans have Boport taking care of our head and cam work on our Lima engines getting us 300-500 RWHP depending on his porting & cam combo. Myself went with Boport's stage 4 head with his 2.1x cam, his twin scroll header and a Garrett gtx ball bearing turbo. With 81 lbs injectors no problem 450-500 RWHP with my 2.3l Lima
If I ever become a Douche Bag with a custom license plate it would say "GROUP B."
